author: Nassim Khadem
title: If Virgin Australia fails, it's 'a bloody disaster'. Who will take its place and do consumers lose out?
description: Until a new airline can come in, pass various regulatory hurdles and establish itself as a formidable competitor to almighty Qantas, the fear is that Australian consumers may lose out with higher fares and reduced flight options.
content:

Virgin Australia's time is almost up.
